c. இனிக்காரியமில்லை. there is no further business. there is no more hope for himsaid of a dying man  
c. இனிநம்மெல்லை. we are now close on our limit; we approach our boundary. இனிப்பிழைக்கிறதா? can he possibly sur vive? (he will certainly die). இனிப்பேசு. now you may speak  
there is no longer any restraint. இனிப்போதும். now there is enough. இனிமேல். hereafter  
at some future time. இனியார்? who else? இனியாற்றாது. i am unable to proceed further (i am altogether exhausted). இனியெங்கேபோவாய்? whither will you go next? what further resource is left you? இனியென்னசெய்வாய்? what can you do further? இனிவேண்டாம். it is needed no longer  
